Annually, many Analysts around the globe report expending up to 80% of the effort and duration of an investigation in &ldquo;wrangling&rdquo; and &ldquo;tidying&rdquo; data into a &ldquo;shape&rdquo; that enables thoughtful, economical analysis. Does this sound like one of your projects?
